OL,3,CFacial reconstruction of man found in
OL,4,Creservoir released by police
OL,6,FA facial reconstruction of a man whose
OL,7,Fbody was found in a reservoir has been
OL,8,Freleased by police more than a year
OL,9,Fafter he was discovered.
OL,11,FThe unidentified man, who was wearing
OL,12,Fa wetsuit, is believed to have been in
OL,13,Fthe water for up to 12 weeks before he
OL,14,Fwas found by a walker at Claerwen
OL,15,FReservoir, Powys, in October 2024.
OL,17,FDyfed-Powys Police have released the
OL,18,Ffacial reconstruction, created by Face
OL,19,FLab at Liverpool John Moores
OL,20,FUniversity, in the hopes someone will
OL,21,Frecognise him.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
