OL,3,CFacial reconstruction of man found in
OL,4,Creservoir released by police
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Anthea Ponting,
OL,7,Fwho has led the investigation, said:
OL,8,F"When the discovery was reported to
OL,9,Fus, we immediately got to work on
OL,10,Festablishing who this man was.
OL,12,F"In the absence of any personal
OL,13,Fbelongings other than the wetsuit he
OL,14,Fwas wearing, no identification
OL,15,Fdocuments or vehicles nearby, we began
OL,16,Fby working with neighbouring police
OL,17,Fforces to conduct checks for missing
OL,18,For wanted people who had not been
OL,19,Ftraced.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773087074
OL,3,CFacial reconstruction of man found in
OL,4,Creservoir released by police
OL,6,F"When this was unsuccessful, we
OL,7,Fextended our inquiries to contact all
OL,8,FUK forces, ran searches through the
OL,9,FPolice National Database, and issued
OL,10,Fbulletins to police overseas through
OL,11,FInterpol.
OL,13,F"We have also searched DNA,
OL,14,Ffingerprint and dental records for
OL,15,Fpotential matches, and issued public
OL,16,Fand media appeals for information.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
