PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773087074
OL,3,CFacial reconstruction of man found in
OL,4,Creservoir released by police
OL,6,F"Each time we have reached out to the
OL,7,Fpublic, we've been provided with some
OL,8,Flines of inquiry to follow-up on, but
OL,9,Funfortunately none have proven to be
OL,10,Fthe key to finding out who this person
OL,11,Fis."
OL,13,FThere were no other items of clothing,
OL,14,Fjewellery or modes of transport in the
OL,15,Farea when the man was found, and he
OL,16,Fhad no distinguishing marks such as
OL,17,Fscars or tattoos.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@DO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
