CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773087074
OL,3,CFacial reconstruction of man found in
OL,4,Creservoir released by police
OL,6,FDyfed-Powys Police said the man was
OL,7,Faged between 30 and 60, around 6ft
OL,8,Ftall, weighing 202-220lb, and of white
OL,9,FEuropean descent.
OL,11,FMs Ponting added: "I urge anyone who
OL,12,Fthinks they might recognise him to
OL,13,Fcome forward.
OL,15,F"This is someone's family member `
OL,16,Fsomeone's loved one ` and I would like
OL,17,Fnothing more than to return him to his
OL,18,Floved ones who might be missing him."
OL,26,@sD@SOUwD@AOUzD@eO]
