OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773087074
OL,3,CFacial reconstruction of man found in
OL,4,Creservoir released by police
OL,6,FAnyone who visited Claerwen Reservoir
OL,7,Fbetween July and October 18 2024 and
OL,8,Fsaw anything that might help
OL,9,Finquiries, or is aware of someone who
OL,10,Fhas not been seen for some time and
OL,11,Fmatches the description, can contact
OL,12,FDyfed-Powys Police on 101.
OL,14,FOr the independent charity
OL,15,FCrimestoppers can be contacted
OL,16,Fanonymously by calling 0800 555111, or
OL,17,Fvisiting crimestoppers-uk.org.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
